You must slay the king! Fight your way through waves of enemies using random weapons given every 10 seconds to get to the king. Gates open up when all the enemies in the area have been killed. The game is saved when you cross a gate

WASD/move
E/interact with upgrade station
space/Slo-mo
Left click/shoot
Right click/dash
Esc/pause
